<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#080610" />
  <meta name="description" content="Clipency is a modern distribution platform helping brands turn creator attention into measurable performance." />
  <title>Clipency | Modern Distribution for Attention</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="landing.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <header class="landing-nav">
    <a class="brand-lockup" href="/">
      <div class="brand-mark">C</div>
      <span>Clipency</span>
    </a>

    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="#what">What we do</a>
      <a href="#clients">For clients</a>
      <a href="#team">Team</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="auth-actions">
      <a class="nav-login" href="/login">Login</a>
      <a class="nav-signup" href="/signup">Sign up</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-glow"></div>

      <div class="hero-copy">
        <div class="eyebrow">NEW AGE MODERN DISTRIBUTION PLATFORM</div>

        <h1>
          We turn internet attention into measurable brand growth.
        </h1>

        <p>
          Clipency connects brands with performance-driven creators who distribute campaigns across social platforms, track output, and earn through results — not inflated influence.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#contact" class="primary-btn">Launch a campaign</a>
          <a href="#what" class="secondary-btn">Explore the system</a>
        </div>

        <div class="proof-strip">
          <div>
            <strong>Performance-first</strong>
            <span>Creators paid on output</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>Global-ready</strong>
            <span>Built for digital campaigns</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>Data-backed</strong>
            <span>Submissions, payouts and insights</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-orbit">
        <div class="orbit-card main-card">
          <span>Campaign Engine</span>
          <strong>Attention → Proof → Payout</strong>
          <p>One operating layer for campaigns, creators and distribution.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="floating-card card-one">
          <small>Creator Network</small>
          <strong>Clippers</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="floating-card card-two">
          <small>Client Goal</small>
          <strong>Reach + Proof</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="floating-card card-three">
          <small>Output</small>
          <strong>Measured Growth</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section intro-grid" id="what">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div class="eyebrow">WHAT CLIPENCY IS</div>
        <h2>Not an agency. Not an influencer marketplace. A distribution system.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="definition-card">
        <h3>For brands</h3>
        <p>Run performance-led campaigns with creators who distribute content, submit proof, and scale attention across platforms.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="definition-card">
        <h3>For creators</h3>
        <p>Discover campaigns, submit content links, track approved performance and earn through measurable output.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="definition-card">
        <h3>For teams</h3>
        <p>Centralise campaign visibility, submissions, approvals, payouts and insights without scattered spreadsheets.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section split-section" id="clients">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">CLIENT INTELLIGENCE</div>
        <h2>Built for brands that want proof, not promises.</h2>
        <p>
          Clipency gives clients a structured way to distribute campaigns through creators while keeping execution measurable. Every campaign can be tracked from brief to submission to payout.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="insight-stack">
        <div class="insight-card">
          <span>01</span>
          <strong>Performance-led campaigns</strong>
          <p>Creators work around campaign goals, not vanity numbers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="insight-card">
          <span>02</span>
          <strong>Proof-based submissions</strong>
          <p>Every creator submits campaign links for review and tracking.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="insight-card">
          <span>03</span>
          <strong>Transparent payouts</strong>
          <p>Approved performance can be connected directly to earnings.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section testimonials-section">
      <div class="section-heading center">
        <div class="eyebrow">TRUST SIGNALS</div>
        <h2>What the market should feel when it sees Clipency.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-grid">
        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <p>“Clipency brings structure to creator distribution. The strongest part is the performance-first thinking behind the platform.”</p>
          <div>
            <strong>Brand Partner</strong>
            <span>Music Campaign</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <p>“Instead of scattered DMs and manual tracking, Clipency gives campaigns a clean operating layer.”</p>
          <div>
            <strong>Growth Team</strong>
            <span>Digital Launch</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <p>“The creator experience feels direct: find a campaign, submit proof, and track performance.”</p>
          <div>
            <strong>Clipper</strong>
            <span>Creator Network</span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section team-section" id="team">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div class="eyebrow">TEAM</div>
        <h2>The people building Clipency’s distribution layer.</h2>
        <p>Department-wise showcase. Replace names and links anytime as the team expands.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="department-block">
        <div class="department-title">
          <span>Leadership</span>
        </div>

        <div class="team-grid">
          <article class="team-card">
            <div class="team-avatar">S</div>
            <h3>Smit Bharat Patil</h3>
            <p>Technology & Platform</p>
            <div class="team-links">
              <a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a>
              <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram">Instagram</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="team-card muted">
            <div class="team-avatar">+</div>
            <h3>Add Founder / Lead</h3>
            <p>Leadership</p>
            <div class="team-links">
              <a href="#">Profile</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="department-block">
        <div class="department-title">
          <span>Technology</span>
        </div>

        <div class="team-grid">
          <article class="team-card muted">
            <div class="team-avatar">T</div>
            <h3>Tech Team Member</h3>
            <p>Frontend / Backend</p>
            <div class="team-links">
              <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
              <a href="#">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="department-block">
        <div class="department-title">
          <span>Marketing & Growth</span>
        </div>

        <div class="team-grid">
          <article class="team-card muted">
            <div class="team-avatar">M</div>
            <h3>Growth Team Member</h3>
            <p>Campaigns / Distribution</p>
            <div class="team-links">
              <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
              <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="department-block">
        <div class="department-title">
          <span>Finance, Legal & Operations</span>
        </div>

        <div class="team-grid">
          <article class="team-card muted">
            <div class="team-avatar">O</div>
            <h3>Operations Team Member</h3>
            <p>Finance / Compliance</p>
            <div class="team-links">
              <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section contact-section" id="contact">
      <div class="contact-copy">
        <div class="eyebrow">START A CAMPAIGN</div>
        <h2>Tell us what you want to distribute.</h2>
        <p>
          Share your campaign goal and we’ll route it into Clipency’s client pipeline. This will later reflect inside the admin dashboard.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-points">
          <span>Campaign planning</span>
          <span>Creator distribution</span>
          <span>Performance review</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <form class="contact-form" id="landing-contact-form">
        <div class="form-grid">
          <label>
            Full name
            <input name="full_name" required placeholder="Your name" />
          </label>

          <label>
            Work email
            <input name="email" type="email" required placeholder="you@company.com" />
          </label>
        </div>

        <div class="form-grid">
          <label>
            Company
            <input name="company" placeholder="Company / Brand" />
          </label>

          <label>
            Role
            <input name="role" placeholder="Founder / Marketer / Manager" />
          </label>
        </div>

        <div class="form-grid">
          <label>
            Budget range
            <select name="budget_range">
              <option value="">Select range</option>
              <option>$500 - $2,000</option>
              <option>$2,000 - $10,000</option>
              <option>$10,000+</option>
              <option>Not sure yet</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label>
            Campaign goal
            <select name="campaign_goal">
              <option value="">Select goal</option>
              <option>Music promotion</option>
              <option>Brand awareness</option>
              <option>Creator distribution</option>
              <option>Product launch</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
          </label>
        </div>

        <label>
          Message
          <textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Tell us about your campaign, target audience, platforms and timeline."></textarea>
        </label>

        <button type="submit">Submit campaign inquiry</button>
        <p id="contact-form-message" class="form-message"></p>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="landing-footer">
    <div>
      <a class="brand-lockup footer-brand" href="/">
        <div class="brand-mark">C</div>
        <span>Clipency</span>
      </a>
      <p>Where attention becomes opportunity.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-socials">
      <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
      <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X</a>
      <a href="mailto:contact@clipency.in">Email</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@supabase/supabase-js@2"></script>
  <script src="supabaseClient.js"></script>
  <script src="landing.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
